column4: Tesla working with AMD to develop chip for self-driving car: CNBC
column5: Electric carmaker Tesla Inc  is working with Advanced Micro Devices Inc  to develop its own artificial intelligence chip for self-driving cars  CNBC reported on Wednesday  citing a source familiar with the matter.

column4: UPDATE 3-Delphi  BlackBerry partner on self-driving software system
column5: Sept 20 Auto suppliers Delphi Automotive Plc and BlackBerry Ltd  will partner on a software operating system for self-driving cars  the companies said on Wednesday.
